quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  53,1,"By the star when it sets:"{1},footnotes:1:1
  53,2,"your companion has neither strayed nor is he deluded;"{1}{2},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2
  53,3,"nor does he speak out of his desire."
  53,4,"This is nothing but a revelation that is conveyed to him,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  53,5,"something that a very powerful one has imparted to him,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  53,6,"one endowed with immense wisdom. He came forth and stood poised,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  53,7,"being on the higher horizon."{1},footnotes:1:1
  53,8,"Then he drew near and hung above suspended,"
  53,9,"until he was two bows' length away, or nearer."{1},footnotes:1:1
  53,10,"Then he revealed to Allah's servant whatever he had to reveal."{1},footnotes:1:1